fiala-sofa;Fiala Sofa;

Fiala is here to help with your design problem. Available in our most popular materials for speedier delivery, this distinguished sofa is elegant, traditional, and crafted by hand, just the way you would expect our preeminent sofas to be.

Colors: Gray.
Materials: Leather.
Dimensions (in.): 84" W x 36" D x 36" H.
  • Perfectly balanced and sturdy.
  • Lightweight and easy to carry for convenience.
  • Durable construction, built to last.
